  "name": "Commander’s Call",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/creatures/eyes/human-single-brown.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP</strong> to command a creature that you can see or that can see or hear you within 5 Spaces to take 1 of the following Actions as a <strong>Reaction </strong>for free.</p><p>You can only use each of the following commands once on each of your turns.</p><ul><li><strong>Attack: </strong>The creature can make an <strong>Attack</strong> with ADV. The creature cannot spend SP, MP, AP or any other resources on this Attack.</li><li><strong>Move: </strong>The creature can move up to their Speed without provoking Opportunity Attacks.</li><li><strong>Dodge:</strong> The creature can take the <strong>Full Dodge </strong>Action.</li></ul>",
